Program: Outlook
Title: A Brush with Death
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrhh
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Stories of near death experiences from disabled singlehanded rower Andrew Halsey and hostage survivor Lizzie Anders. Also, another story from someone making a new life abroad. Finally, overcoming the fear of maths, Professor Keith Devlin explains how. Presenter: Frederick Dove.